name: KinuGitsune's Debut!
description:
Come experience the debut of the one and only KinuGitsune. Learn the lore! Find love! Fight for survival??? Only one of these is actually accurate! Enjoy a deeply complex branching story featuring THREE (3) unique choices to make! And then tune in to the fox herself at twitch.tv/kinugitsune!

Music from the Fate/Stay Night OST
